{"tid":1905654,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[極危險] 米蘭看秀回韓確診再加一　宋慧喬、IU、木村光希也有去","createTime":"2020-03-01T11:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T18:41:07.000Z","uid":34643,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8af5fe50509e8705ada1bf892bc308f1b13a197e","tid":1905654,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:45:47.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情在南韓、義大利發威，昨確定一名曾到米蘭參加時裝週的演藝圈工作人員確診後，29日再爆出另一名同行人員確診，網友比對時間線索發現應是歌手請夏的公司職員。而上週曾出席時裝週的藝人還包含BLACKPINK的LISA、NU&rsquo;EST的黃旼炫、朴敏英、韓藝瑟、宋慧喬、IU、木村光希、山下智久、威爾史密斯等人，日、韓、歐美地區演藝圈將陷入恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n韓媒《OSEN》報導，某工作人員B陪著歌手A到國外拍畫報，回國後B疑似出現武漢肺炎症狀，結果確診，也透露該歌手A發片在即。網友根據報導線索，以及政府公布首爾廣津區確診首例曾於2月19至24日赴義大利，請夏恰巧上週赴米蘭看秀與拍畫報，也於29日出新歌，種種跡象不謀而合，而她發文報平安時，僅要歌迷注意健康，未對謠言作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n29日晚間媒體再報導，第2例確診的女性，是看到B某確診後，因與他接觸過也去篩檢，沒想到中鏢。據悉，該女回韓國後除了進公司，還曾到美容院、醫美診所、餐廳等地，雖然表示全程配戴口罩，但這些地點正進行消毒，接觸者也已自主隔離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外，參加米蘭時裝週的藝人，都會住在同一家飯店以便行動，除了請夏，BLACKPINK的LISA、NU&rsquo;EST的黃旼炫、朴敏英、韓藝瑟、宋慧喬、IU、木村光希、山下智久、威爾史密斯等人也有出席，各國演藝圈恐陷入大規模感染。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1582992145-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a-696x464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F1582992145-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a-696x464.jpg&h=3d2d19f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49d0ee6433658acec19c0bff9d78cd1fb1af72f9","tid":1905654,"uid":29816,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901715de3428eb64511d3f43cff9a3cb197436a6","tid":1905654,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"no<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a609ae93c750d85c300f8894f5628fbb7ee036","tid":1905654,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"064633feeb52c38225a8f178fc0f437d3d59ee1a","tid":1905654,"uid":216704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f619e6fae08e2e279f85c57d1fd3ae7fd08e4f","tid":1905654,"uid":226952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"唔好有事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我的知恩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9670051e88f837bac7e06be59a549932173e6f","tid":1905654,"uid":256383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"諗起同iu打車輪個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328f92c20b26b752c5ec754abaa7fcc4f396b2be","tid":1905654,"uid":224698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013c12fb820bbd14a837f38a23ed046907e74338","tid":1905654,"uid":256383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f9670051e88f837bac7e06be59a549932173e6f","tid":1905654,"uid":256383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:43.0